data.description: Well Maintained Brick Ranch Home on an absolutely beautiful lot.  You will never need to leave home with an large detached office with heating and cooling and a one car garage, fenced-in yard with relaxing deck and patio PLUS an amazing pool with wrap around deck. Large driveway with plenty of parking and a carport.  Family room has gas log fireplace. Hardwoods in Dining Room, Family Room, Hallway & two secondary bedrooms. Dining Room Features patio doors leading on to peaceful deck. Master Bedroom has new carpet and a full bath.
